## Quick Reference: Design ↔ Code Translations

| Design Concept | Code Equivalent |
|---|---|
| Figma Component | React Component |
| Component Variant | Props / CSS class variant |
| Auto Layout | Flexbox / CSS Grid |
| Design Tokens / Variables | CSS Custom Properties / Tailwind Config |
| Component Instance | JSX Element (`<Button />`) |
| Nested Frames | Component Composition / `children` prop |
| Prototype Interactions | Event Handlers (`onClick`, `onChange`) |
| Page Structure | Next.js Routes + Layouts |
| Figma Styles | Tailwind Utility Classes / Theme |
| Responsive Constraints | Media Queries / Responsive Breakpoints |
| Component Properties | TypeScript Interface / Props |